125
00:10:45,550 --> 00:10:48,770
[Mr. Bai Bakery]

126
00:10:47,870 --> 00:10:48,960
Mr. Bai. B-a-i.

127
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,600
I'm Bai Lang. This is my shop.

128
00:10:50,620 --> 00:10:51,270
Got it?

129
00:10:52,670 --> 00:10:53,630
You're Bai Lang?

130
00:10:53,750 --> 00:10:54,510
Yes.

131
00:10:56,220 --> 00:10:57,320
Are you really Bai Lang?

132
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:57,840
Yeah.

133
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:02,230
You do look like him.

134
00:11:02,510 --> 00:11:04,120
What do you mean? I am him.

135
00:11:05,550 --> 00:11:06,860
Aren't you dead?

136
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:08,350
You're the one who's dead.

137
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:11,160
Am I dreaming?

138
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:16,260
If he didn't die,

139
00:11:16,670 --> 00:11:17,730
