It's not the hospital.

149
00:11:32,790 --> 00:11:33,910
There aren't drugs for sale.

150
00:11:36,580 --> 00:11:38,340
Why did you give me the house?

151
00:11:39,080 --> 00:11:39,960
Miss.

152
00:11:40,280 --> 00:11:42,130
If you keep this up,

153
00:11:42,160 --> 00:11:43,880
I'll have to take you to the police station.

154
00:11:44,580 --> 00:11:45,180
No.

155
00:11:45,210 --> 00:11:46,690
You really gave me the house.

156
