-Stop!

164
00:11:56,870 --> 00:11:57,910
Stop!

165
00:12:02,390 --> 00:12:03,260
Bai Lang.

166
00:12:03,400 --> 00:12:04,690
-Sir, are you okay?
-Are you okay?

167
00:12:04,710 --> 00:12:05,710
I'm fine. I'm fine.

