Come on, slowly.

170
00:12:08,130 --> 00:12:09,660
[Monday, July 27, Year of Jiayin]

171
00:12:08,870 --> 00:12:09,900
Year of Jiayin?

172
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:11,040
I'm sorry.

173
