174
00:12:12,240 --> 00:12:12,720
Stop!

175
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:13,790
-Stop! Stop!
-We have to go!

176
00:12:13,810 --> 00:12:15,480
-Stop! Stop!
-You'd better stop!

177
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:16,720
-Go after him!
-Stop!

178
00:12:17,680 --> 00:12:19,250
-You'd better stop!
-Stop!

179
00:12:19,390 --> 00:12:20,670
