00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:11,500
I really traveled back in time.

192
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,200
Mr. Bai Lang.

193
00:13:15,670 --> 00:13:16,450
Mr. Bai Lang!

194
00:13:16,480 --> 00:13:17,510
It's really you!

195
00:13:17,630 --> 00:13:18,000
Hey.

196
00:13:18,280 --> 00:13:18,990
Don't you think

