233
00:14:58,030 --> 00:14:58,870
I'm fine.

234
00:14:59,910 --> 00:15:02,870
Why'd you mess with their gang leader's woman?

235
00:15:03,420 --> 00:15:05,170
You sure are bold.

236
00:15:05,930 --> 00:15:07,010
Actually, I was just

237
00:15:07,040 --> 00:15:08,310
covering for my buddy.

238
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:10,800
