239
00:15:10,960 --> 00:15:13,240
No, they won't be able to find me soon.

240
00:15:14,670 --> 00:15:15,700
Why?

241
00:15:16,130 --> 00:15:18,970
Because I'm about to sell this shop

242
00:15:19,090 --> 00:15:20,240
