243
00:15:20,340 --> 00:15:21,790
How can they find me?

244
00:15:22,670 --> 00:15:23,720
Sell the shop?

245
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:25,300
You're not making cakes anymore?

246
00:15:25,390 --> 00:15:26,930
Are there any customers here?

247
00:15:32,510 --> 00:15:33,980
No way.

248
00:15:34,910 --> 00:15:36,260
Did you make this?

249
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:54,510
Not bad.

250
00:15:57,270 --> 00:15:58,660
You don't have to comfort me.

251
00:15:58,760 --> 00:15:59,580
I know.

252
00:15:59,750 --> 00:16:02,340
I know that I might not be cut out for this.

253
00:16:03,840 --> 00:16:05,440
No way, Mr. Bai Lang.

254
00:16:05,470 --> 00:16:07,100
You're my idol.

255
00:16:07,270 --> 00:16:09,090
If I hadn't eaten your cake,

256
00:16:09,200 --> 00:16:11,750
