257
00:16:16,720 --> 00:16:17,630
That's not important.

258
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:19,150
What matters is

259
00:16:19,790 --> 00:16:20,880
you have to trust me.

260
00:16:21,120 --> 00:16:22,530
I'm from the future.

261
00:16:23,630 --> 00:16:25,270
In the near future,

262
00:16:25,300 --> 00:16:27,470
