279
00:17:21,240 --> 00:17:22,920
That's your secret recipe.

280
00:17:23,250 --> 00:17:24,010
Otherwise,

281
00:17:24,040 --> 00:17:25,599
why's the whole city obsessed

282
00:17:25,619 --> 00:17:26,770
